msgstr "this was his killer? "

msgctxt "sn22.85:15.9"
msgid "Yadāpi naṃ rahogataṃ viditvā tiṇhena satthena jīvitā voropeti, tadāpi so vadhakova. "
msgstr "And when, knowing he was alone, they took his life with a sharp knife, weren’t they a killer then, "

msgctxt "sn22.85:15.10"
msgid "Vadhakañca pana santaṃ na aññāsi: "
msgstr "though he didn’t know that "

msgctxt "sn22.85:15.11"
msgid "‘vadhako me’”ti. "
msgstr "this was his killer?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.85:15.12"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti. "
msgstr "“Yes, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.85:15.13"
msgid "“Evameva kho, āvuso, assutavā puthujjano ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido ariyadhamme avinīto, sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido sappurisadhamme avinīto "
msgstr "“In the same way, an uneducated ordinary person has not seen the noble ones, and is neither skilled nor trained in the teaching of the noble ones. They’ve not seen good persons, and are neither skilled nor trained in the teaching of the good persons. "

msgctxt "sn22.85:15.14"
msgid "rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ; attani vā rūpaṃ, rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ. "
msgstr "They regard form as self, self as having form, form in self, or self in form. "

