msgid "Tassime pañcupādānakkhandhā upetā upādinnā dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "And when you’ve gotten involved with and grasped these five grasping aggregates, they lead to your lasting harm and suffering. "

