msgid "Tassime pañcupādānakkhandhā anupetā anupādinnā dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "And when you’re not attracted to and don’t grasp these five grasping aggregates, they lead to your lasting welfare and happiness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.85:28.7"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, āvuso sāriputta, hoti yesaṃ āyasmantānaṃ tādisā sabrahmacārino anukampakā atthakāmā ovādakā anusāsakā. "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, this is how it is when you have such venerables as spiritual companions to advise and instruct you out of kindness and compassion. "

msgctxt "sn22.85:28.8"
msgid "Idañca pana me āyasmato sāriputtassa dhammadesanaṃ sutvā anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuttan”ti. "
msgstr "And after hearing this teaching by Venerable Sāriputta, my mind is freed from the defilements by not grasping.” "

